    {
      "id": "stage-02",
      "order": 2,
      "title": "Triángulos por ángulos",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Triángulos por ángulos</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css\">\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height:1.6; padding: 18px 16px 60px; }\n    h1,h2,h3 { margin: 0.2em 0 0.4em; }\n    .pill { display: inline-block; padding: 0.2em 0.6em; border-radius: 999px; background: #eee; font-size: 0.9em; margin-right: 6px; }\n    .tip { background: #f0fbff; border-left: 4px solid #6ac8ff; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .ex { background: #fff7ed; border-left: 4px solid #ffb86b; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .note { background: #f6f8fa; border-left: 4px solid #c9d1d9; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px,1fr)); gap: 14px; }\n    .card { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; }\n    svg { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display:block; margin: 8px auto; }\n    .q { margin: 8px 0; }\n    code.katex-display { font-size: 1.05em; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<h1>Tipos de triángulos por <em>ángulos</em></h1>\n<p>En todo triángulo la suma de ángulos interiores es $$\\alpha + \\beta + \\gamma = 180^\\circ.$$</p>\n<div class=\"grid\">\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h3>Acutángulo</h3>\n    <p>Todos sus ángulos son agudos ($&lt;90^\\circ$).</p>\n    \n<svg viewBox=\"0 0 240 170\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-label=\"ΔABC\">\n  <polygon points=\"40,150 130,20 220,150\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n  <text x=\"18\" y=\"160\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#374151\">A</text>\n  <text x=\"118\" y=\"18\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#374151\">B</text>\n  <text x=\"220\" y=\"160\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#374151\">C</text>\n</svg>\n\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h3>Rectángulo</h3>\n    <p>Tiene un ángulo recto ($90^\\circ$). Se cumple el teorema de Pitágoras:</p>\n    <p class=\"tip\">$$a^2 + b^2 = c^2$$</p>\n    \n<svg viewBox=\"0 0 240 170\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-label=\"ΔABC\">\n  <polygon points=\"20,140 20,20 220,140\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n  <text x=\"18\" y=\"160\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#374151\">A</text>\n  <text x=\"118\" y=\"18\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#374151\">B</text>\n  <text x=\"220\" y=\"160\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#374151\">C</text>\n</svg>\n\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h3>Obtusángulo</h3>\n    <p>Tiene un ángulo obtuso ($&gt;90^\\circ$).</p>\n    \n<svg viewBox=\"0 0 240 170\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-label=\"ΔABC\">\n  <polygon points=\"20,140 160,110 220,140\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fb923c\" stroke-width=\"3\" />\n  <text x=\"18\" y=\"160\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#374151\">A</text>\n  <text x=\"118\" y=\"18\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#374151\">B</text>\n  <text x=\"220\" y=\"160\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#374151\">C</text>\n</svg>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\ndocument.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n  renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n    delimiters: [\n      {left: \"$$\", right: \"$$\", display: true},\n      {left: \"$\", right: \"$\", display: false}\n    ]\n  });\n});\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>",
